\id GLO
\h Memba Walsamona Plalmoa
\toc1 Memba Walsamona Plalmoa Honamba moamba memba novol velohvpa, Sesoana moana plalmoa. Englisnamba pimba osm uv,
\toc2 Memba Walsamona Plalmoa
\mt1 Memba Walsamona Plalmoa
\mt2 Honamba moamba memba novol velohvpa, Sesoana moana plalmoa. Englisnamba pimba osm uv,\bdit glossary\bdit*, memba osm, \bdit little dictionary\bdit*
\li1 \bd Aisaia \bd*\rq (Matiu 3:3 / Aposel 8:30 / Rom 9:27-29)\rq*
\li2 Aisaiava mongo mendekli moashulnindrini lohna Sesoana. Mendah Kristusva lohnamoa, Aisaiava doara moamba wulluhvna, ona, si os sewonamba venavav Kristusmba.
\li1 \bd Alta / hon songowol vena. \bd*\rq (Stat 8:20 / Matiu 5:23) (alta bilong lotu)\rq*
\li2 Memba honseng suwem nosram sengalm. Noava tatam losang venamba, wo honsengra suwerava wohweisumblolona, osm Yawe Sesoam sembayang vene.
\li2 Sismba Sesoa Yutanindm wohtna, altaseng besina besal vinu kam. \it (Kisim Bek 27).\it*
\li1 \bd Aonghalmahalnind \bd*\rq (Matiu 4:18 / 5:1-2) (disaipel)\rq*
\li2 Memba Yesusna hellelnind indkumbi, ten nihra hev wonlohmana vevnam. No indhanahovrava, mongo 12pelara indhanamba lovahvna, os nengsmoa uv hemba, moalamangnind o aposel \it (Matiu 10:1-2).\it*
\li1 \bd Apel \bd*\rq (Matiu 23:35 / Hipru 11:4) (Abel)\rq*
\li2 Apelva Atamna ombol lohna, Keinna boasalal lohna. Keinmba Apelmba helvakomandhana. \it (Stat 4:1-8) \it*Indhanariniva owalmba helvakomandhalmba, men honisna evena.
\li1 \bd Apraham \bd*\rq (Stat 12:1-25:18 / Hipru 6:13-15)\rq*
\li2 Aprahamba Israelnindna tomonal luhunna. Seilva nihilva henamba \bd Apram\bd* maim sevra ovrivna, memba osm uvna, kuwul wulluhunv. Hengava Sesoa weihaloh vremnana, Apraham maimba, memba osm uvna, kuwul wulluhunv indkumbina.
\li2 Doara heva doa Sesoava Aprahamba waiishona, osva yetindiva si petha nemelmba vaohuthuvav. Yeoa pevna pethamoa wuleihalahaphorava, dom no petharam gao. Wo diva no petharava Sesoava hemba henga waiishovna, omnana, yetindiva si katindilm avav, heva heoa kamoa keknam undnahonam amnavra.
\li2 Apraham \bd Saram\bd* vrana, heva os himba phal avna. Wo doa mundkola vewolvna. Heva os Sesoa hemba kolvrena, otollangla velmba, \bd Isakm\bd* awona.
\li2 \bd Isakva\bd* mendekli venamba, ongamba vrana, \bd Repekam\bd* \it (Stat 25—27). \it*Wo ombolsambla elohmanana, vena\bd Esau\bd* eva \bd Yakop\bd*. Yakopna nihilva mongova \bd Israel\bd*, noinda Yutanindva eva osva nengsmoa uvna, Israelnind \it (Stat 28:13-15 / Rom 9:10).\it*
\li2 Yakoppa dombtana sambla ongamba, vena \bd Lea\bd* hevm eva \bd Reselm\bd*, moasalalm. Wo osoa ongalna andranind unguvlirinisamblam dombtana, \bd Bilham\bd* eva \bd Silpam\bd* \it (Stat 29—35).\it*
\li2 Yakopnamba ombolva 12pelara phomnana, wo nomba simbepolva phonamba, hemba pivva os nengsmoa uv, Israelnind, nomini ten 12pelara aratindi phonam. \it (Poaitamoa 7:4—8)\it*
\li2 Mongova nomba Yakopna ombolva lohna, nihilva henamba \bd Yuta\bd*. Noinda Israelnindna mongona nihilva luhunv, Yutanind. Sisva \bd Devit\bd* king kuwulva no Yutatindirini lohna, wo eva sisnonoava \bd Yesus Kristusva\bd* nomini lohnata.
\li2 Noinda pimba notindiva osva nengsmoa uv, Sesoana awothowolnind. Vei Apraham hev, vei Isak, vei Yakop, vei Devit, vei Maria, veiva, Yesus Kristus hev.
\li1 \bd Arana ombol \bd*\rq (Daniel 7:13-14 / Matiu 24:31 / Mak 8:31) (pikinini bilong man)\rq*
\li2 Hona moarava Yesusva os ona, kava vei, tanamolnam indhanarinielm lohv, eva tanamolnam Sesoalm lohv.
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Yawe\bd* eva \bd Memba kata ka\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Ararat \bd*\rq (Stat 8:4)\rq*
\li2 Memba mongo petha.
\li1 \bd Aron \bd*\rq (Kisim Bek 28 / Aposel 7:40 / Hipru 5:4)\rq*
\li2 Aronmba Yakopna bueindil lohna, Livaina ombol, wo Aronna boasalalva Moses lohna. Sesoava Aronmba kikih vrena, hevna sembayang andranindrinielm, os alvna hemba, pris. Omnana, yetindiangas honaoa andraoa kamoa vewuvmona veno.
\li2 Sembayang andranindna englamokolnind, os hemba nengsmoa uv, Livai.
\li2 Mosesiva Aroniva wonepholaha ephona hevna Israelnindmba Isipethariniva, Sesoana hevna moara. \it (Kisim Bek 12:31)\it*
\li1 \bd Atam \bd*\rq (Stat 1:26 / Luk 3:38) (Adam)\rq*
\li2 Seilnonoava Sesoava Atamsna vena pethanamba. Atamba osm uv, indhana.
\li2 Polva moalamangnindriniva os ona, Yesus Kristus os lohna, sismini Atamsna. \it (1 Korin 15:45)\it* Manara, seilmini Atamba indkokla venamba, wo pimba indkumbimba noinda dalv. Heva os sismini Atamba pimba daheinna, wo noinda pimba undnamba av yunalmba, memba pimba hemba keknamba undnahonamba amnavpa.
\li1 \bd Bal \bd*\rq (Rom 11:4) (giaman god Bal)\rq*
\li2 Balva mongo Sesoa daspol, noi ten ungund sembayang velvohmanavnam Israelnindna pethara. Elsusva ungundva deisumbaisuv velvohvna Israelnindmba, Sesoanonoamba meis haravhueimnivnamba, Balm okulivna. Noinda Sesoava Israelnindmba nomba wusprunvna.
\li1 \bd Balam \bd*\rq (Namba 22:21-35 / 2 Pita 2:15 / Yut 11 / Poaitamoa 2:14)\rq*
\li2 Balamba mongo moashulnindrini lohna. Wo nonamba Moapnindva daos ohovna Israelnindmongo, Moapnindna kuwulva wulluhunna, Balak. Wo Balakva Balamba omnana, yeoa Israelnindmoa kikpulna polothunu, osm heoa owolakovra daosmoa.
\li2 Balamba donkisra gavna monam, osm velm, heva os Sesoana ovsongolnindrini monam kelvhoamnana. Donki nonglana ovsongolnindrinimba, heva os Balamba hevpa owai, nonglanamoa. Hev phona, donkim helve, osm venavna, gao. Noinda donkiva indhanarinimsna moamba ishomnavna Balamba, yimba indkokla vei \it (Namba 22—24).\it*
\li2 Balamba es eva Israelnindmba ata vinta, manara, Sesoava doa hemba doara awothowol vena. Balamba di mindnam und vevna, noinda himba Balakna moamba wohengvna.
\li1 \bd Bapel \bd*\rq (Stat 11:9) (Babel)\rq*
\li2 Honamba moamba memba osm lohv, indakondamomba wulbukethav.
\li1 \bd Bapilon \bd*\rq (Stat 10:10 / Matiu 1:11) (Babilonia)\rq*
\li2 Memba kota-mendekli. Seilva nemetva Bapilonnindva wulnaongla phonamba, ehelvowolanamba Israelnindmongo, wo kuvhoawol vina hemba. Wo himba Israelnindmba ninginguavna hevna andranindilm, wo os wulavna hemba diva, venamba, 70pelara tahonmba luhunvna.
\li2 Yon moalamangnindrini pimba olhmonamba olhinv, os Sesoana ungundva si Bapilonnindmsna avav. \it (Poaitamoa 1718)\it* Memba osm honamba, owaimomolva himba Sesoamba ningminivmoa.
\li2 Pitava wevsakoklam ishomnavna Sisakuwulnam Romnindnam, noinda himba Romkota os olhvna, Bapilon. Manara, himba Kristustindimba wohwangtumb gavnam yunalm \it (1 Pita 5:13).\it*
\li1 \bd Barak \bd*\rq (Hipru 11:32)\rq*
\li2 Barakva mongo Israelnindna mendekli kuwul luhunna. He daosrava miva lohmana vinvna \it (Hetman 4—5).\it*
\li1 \bd Bea \bd*\rq (Poaitamoa 13:2)\rq*
\li2 Beava mongo sungeittata, heva os mongnindna pethara luhungu vinv, huiva PNGrava owai. Englavoskava henamba nuveskol vilunv tokol.
\li1 \bd Bensamin \bd*\rq (Aposel 13:21 / Rom 11:1 / Vilipai 3:5)\rq*
\li2 Bensaminmba Yakopna kalalnonoa lohna. Wo noinda mongnindva nomba Israelnindnamba os nengsmoa uv, Bensamintindi.
\li1 \bd Besalnemelmoa \bd*\rq (Matiu 4:16) (gutnius)\rq*
\li2 Memba Sesoana nemelmoa besal.
\li1 \bd Betel \bd*\rq (Stat 12:8)\rq*
\li2 Memba moamba osm lohv, Sesoana deuv.
\li1 \bd Betlehem \bd*\rq (Matiu 2:1)\rq*
\li2 Avalva Devitmba lengna hona kembellava, wo sism Mariava Yesusmba lengna hona kembellava, manara, noinda himba Devit kuwultindirini lohna.
\li1 \bd Deliam \bd*\rq (Stat 2:12)\rq*
\li2 Memba tinen, himba besal teihnungna vilov.
\li1 \bd Devit \bd*\rq (Matiu 1:117 / Luk 3:31)\rq*
\li2 Devitva Yesina kalal lohna, nomba Yutatindirini. Himba kuwul besal wulluhunna Israelnindmba, wo he kuvhoawol vinvna nomba owalna andramba, vei sisminim eva doaraminim \it (1 Samuel 16:11).\it*
\li2 Himba Goliatmba honnamba lipiavna \it (1 Samuel 17).\it* Devitva Sesoamangas undva vevna, noinda himba sangalva ovovrawol venavna, nonamba okolalmba. Pimba os ningthiv, Buk Song o Psalms. Sesoava moamba ovlahana, os Kristusva si lohvav Devittindirini, wo honamba os wohphona, ten Sesoa hev onam \it (Rom 1:3 / Poaitamoa 5:5).\it*
\li1 \bd Elaisa \bd*\rq (Luk 4:27) (Elisa)\rq*
\li2 Elaisava mongo Sesoana moashulnindrini. Himba Elaitana owalna vuhera lohmanana \it (2 King 2:118).\it*
\li1 \bd Elaita \bd*\rq (Mak 9:4 / Rom 11:2 / Yems 5:17) (Elaija)\rq*
\li2 Elaitava mongova Sesoana moashulnindrini lohna. Himba mendekliandrava vevna, manara, Sesoana keknasowolva heindava ambo lotholohvna. Yesusva Yon Baptaismba olhmona olhinvna, ona, Elaitamsna himba lohna \it (Matiu 11:14).\it*
\li1 \bd Epraim \bd*\rq (Stat 41:50-52) (Efraim)\rq*
\li2 Himba Yosepna kalal lohna. Plalva os lohv, Sesoa kamba otolva holvoraohv.
\li1 \bd Esau \bd*\rq (Stat 25:25 / Rom 9:13 / Hipru 11:20 / 12:16-17) (Iso)\rq*
\li2 Memba moamba osm lohv, talna. Isakna ombolsambla elohna, vena Esau eva Yakop. Avalva dendina lengwolna hemba, yivaltowondva Esauva, boasalalva Yakop. Noinda Esau si vaohothovav aralna puwulva. Heva os ponm indkokla vovhoavnamba, hev omnana hevna boasalalm, inne kam vraho, daha ye aranapuwuloa vaohotho, kava owai. Osva himba nengnamoa nomba Sesoana moamba, temba awothowolnamba aralm eva yivaltowondalm.
\li1 \bd Fik denwit \bd*\rq (Luk 21:29) (diwai fik)\rq*
\li2 Fikva movolva besal kethav. Noinda Yutanindva esvema endhavna, hlalm.
\li1 \bd Giteon \bd*\rq (Hipru 11:32) (Gideon)\rq*
\li2 Giteonmba eva mongo kuwul luhunna Israelnindnamba. Himba Sesoam keknam undnahonam lohmanana, noinda himba Sesoamba osahmanavna, kam kolvro, daosm nonapopolm wulpholm. Wo doa Giteonmba hevna valgonindmba deisumbi vohavna daosramba. Diva ungundva pomsna olvna, heva os Israelnind hemba wohwangtumbna yunalm \it (Hetman 6—8).\it*
\li1 \bd Gol \bd*\rq (Matiu 2:11 / Poaitamoa 1:12 / 3:18 / 21:21) (gol / amas)\rq*
\li2 Golva dina aval, wo besal enesmosal hevm. Noinda Sesoava Yutanindmba wohtna, manam manam vewol viu golnangas, nonam kam sembayangnam okuluvmona velm tempelduvrava.
\li2 Yon moalamangnindriniva pimba olhluhunvna golmba, nonamba himba pimba numhawol vevnamba, ovna, manimani sna nalohv senamba diva Sesoaindava murapetava.
\li1 \bd Gomora\bd*
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm Lotm eva Sotom.)
\li1 \bd Grik\bd*
\li2 Grikva mongo petha dihelvna, kotava mendekli lohna Atens. Griknindva manam manam nonoarangas avna, noinda mongnindva hemba wivewol ovolvohvna, wo osoa himba noinda Griknindna moamba nonorava avna.
\li2 Yesusna besal nemelmomba seilva Griknindna moana novol vewol vina tombairava.
\li1 \bd Hakar \bd*\rq (Galesia 4:24-25)\rq*
\li2 Hakarva Sarana andranind unguvlirini ana, Saramba nomba Aprahamna ongalputowa avna. Saramba phal avna, noinda himba Apraham wuhhona, osva wou, wailiu Hakarmoa, memba pina wevsa. Wo os evena, Sara ten unnam, wo doa Hakarva otolm lengna Aprahamna, Ismaelm awona.
\li2 Heva os Sesoava nomba otolmba os venavna, memba kana moarava owai. Heva os sism Saramba hevpa otolmba lengna, Isakm awona. Wo Sesoava nomba otolmba os venavna, memba kana moara pholana.
\li1 \bd Haleluya \bd*\rq (Poaitamoa 19:1) (haleluya)\rq*
\li2 Memba Israelnindna moana, osm uv, pioa Sesoamoa okolalohra! Israelnindna moamba, pimba os ningthiv, Hiprumoa.
\li2 Hosana \it (Matiu 21:9)\it* Memba mongawamoa, pioa Sesoamoa okulivra.
\li1 \bd Herot\bd*
\li2 Hona tombaira Herotva sambla sambla os lovahv.
\li3 \bdit (1) Hona Herotva\bdit* kuwul wulluhunna Yutanindnamba, nonamba Mariava Yesusmba lengvnamba. Nonoanindva Yesusm nonglalm ambvna, Herotm os osihminina, yimba nonora lohvma, hi Yesusva avalva lengliav? \it (Matiu 2:1-2 / Luk 1:5)\it*
\li3 \bdit (2) Hona Herotva\bdit*, nihilva henamba mongova Antipas, wo himba kuwul wulluhunvna Galili provinsnindnam, nonamba Yesusva diva Sesoana moamba ishomana vinvnamba. Himba Yon Baptaisna kuwulva os kovhoana diva buiduvrava \it (Mak 6:1429).\it* Nonamba Yutanindna kuwulva Yesusmba waiishuvnamba, hona Herot Antipasina waiishuvnata \it (Luk 23:6-12).\it*
\li3 \bdit (3) Hona Herotva\bdit*, nihilva henamba mongova Akripa 1, himba val vewul vina Yesusnindmongova. Himba helvakomandhana Yemsmba moalamangnindrinimba, nomba Yonna etelmba \it (Aposel 12:1-23).\it*
\li3 \bdit (4) Hona Herotva\bdit*, nihilva henamba mongova Akripa 2, himba Pol moalamangnindrinina wetatmomba hellevna, nonamba Yutanindna kuwulva Polmba waiishuvnamba wetatmorava \it (Aposel 25:13—26 / 26:19, 27—32).\it*
\li2 Honamba Herotva sambla samblava memba lovahvnamba, himba mongnind, Yutanindna meisungund, wo himba aknandhamana vevna Romduangmongova, noinda Romduangva hemba awowol vina, kuwulm ilvahinilm Yutanindnam.
\li1 \bd Hiprunind \bd*\rq (Yona 1:9 / Vilipai 3:5 / Poaitamoa 9:7)\rq*
\li2 Memba moamba Yonanamba, himba osm ovna, Aprahamtindirini kava lohv, ten noi doara Sesoam Yawem keknam undnahonam lohmanavnam. Israelnindva hevmba os nengsmoa uvna, kava Hiprunind, eva kana moamba Hiprumoa luhunv.
\li1 \bd Hutov kueiv. \bd*\rq (Stat 17:9-14 / Rom 2:25 / Galesia 5:2 / 1 Korin 7:19)\rq*
\li2 Yutanindva os vivna, otolva simba 8pelarava avalva waivevnamba, doa hutovpa kovhueimnivna, osm yimba memba Yutanindrininonoa. Manara, doara doa Sesoava Aprahamba ishomnana honamba osmba velmba.
\li1 \bd Innemba Isipnindna \bd*\rq (Stat 41:46—49)\rq*
\li2 Memba wit, witva brasna nihna.
\li1 \bd Isak \bd*\rq (Stat 17:19 / 21:3 / Aposel 7:8 / Rom 9:7 / Hipru 11:9)\rq*
\li2 Isakva Aprahamina Saraina ombol luhunna, Yakopna aral. Isakmba osm awuna, los ov.
\li1 \bd Isip \bd*\rq (Stat 12:10 / Aposel 7:34-40 / Hipru 11:27)\rq*
\li2 Isippa mongo petha, noi di ten murapeta luhunvna Yutanindna pethara. Tahonmba mindnam pekhua vungeinna, nonamba Isipnindva hemba wulavnamba andranindilmba diva Isiprava. Wo doa Sesoava esvema vinvna Isipnindmba, wo os Yutanindva pulvona nominiva.
\li1 \bd Israel \bd*\rq (Stat 32:22—28)\rq*
\li2 Yutanindna tomonalva doarava luhunna, Yakop. Sesoa hemba henga awona, Israel, memba osm uv, Sesoai hevm epishawolvna. Yakopna 12pelara ombolva lovahna, wo hemba os nengsmoa uvna, Israelnind, nihilva mongova, Yutanind.
\li2 Sismba himba Isipriniva vinamba, anganamba, ungundnamini muehvina Keinanpethava hevelm, nom wohengivna moam, Sesoa ten doara ishomnanam Apraham. Wo Keinan maimba sevra ovralmba wuleihivna, Israelm maim sevra ovrivna.
\li1 \bd Iv \bd*\rq (Stat 3:20 / 2 Korin 11:3 / 1 Timoti 2:13)\rq*
\li2 Ivpa Atamna ongal ana. Ivmba osm awona, indhanana indkumbina aval einv. Atamina Ivina towandva men, vei Kein, Apel eva Set.
\li1 \bd Kamel \bd*\rq (Matiu 3:4 / Luk 18:25)\rq*
\li2 Kamelva mendekli tata vilov. Nemetva Yutanindva daoh vrevna, osm vevna, noinam hevm angalm, eva kinm ianga velm.
\li1 \bd Katekis o gurugama \bd*\rq (ol saveman bilong lo)\rq*
\li2 Hena andrava numhowolalm luhunvna Israelnindm, moam nom ten Sesoa Mosesm vraohnam. Mindnamba himba Varisinindilm lovahvna, noinda himba Yesusmongova ahnam lovahwolvna.
\li1 \bd Kein \bd*\rq (Stat 4:116 / Hipru 11:4 / 1 Yon 3:12 / Yut 11)\rq*
\li2 Memba moamba os hilliv Hiprumonamba, kava doa lengei. Keinmba Atamina Ivina yivaltowond luhunna. Himba hevna boasalalmba Apelmba helvakomandhana. Noinda Sesoava hemba nihra suwesumbulna saihana, osm indhanamba nunglivrava, uvra, indkoklana lohv, heva os Sesoava hemba dandana vrev.
\li1 \bd Keinanpetha \bd*\rq (Stat 11:31 / 12:5 / 13:12 / Aposel 13:19) (Kenan)\rq*
\li2 Keinanpethava noita, ten Sesoa doara ovrahonam Apraham. Yutanindva hengava os weihaloh vrivna, Israelnindna petha o Israel. Seilva ungund vaohuthuna, wo heva os Yutanindva Yosuanambara doa muehvina nomba pethava.
\li1 \bd Kilumbshoav \bd*\rq (Matiu 26:28-29 / Rom 3:21) (baim bek)\rq*
\li2 Honamba moamba osm lohv, pimba indkoklal avna Sesoana novrava, wo Yesusva doa pimba kilumb shoawol vena, osm ora lehra windel av.
\li1 \bd Kora \bd*\rq (Namba 16 / Yut 11)\rq*
\li2 Koramba doara lohvna nonamba Mosesna novrava. Koramba Mosesi Aronim unvna, yengasva vuhemba kekalvho evevravavmoa, kam ewulihamno, ka prisalmoa luhuni Israelnindnaoa. Heva os Sesoava onamoa, wo noinda pethava puvkonamba, wo doa Koratatanamba wohtolpena, dalalmba.
\li1 \bd Kristus \bd*\rq (Matiu 1:1 / 16:16 / Yon 1:41 / Aposel 5:42 / 9:22)\rq*
\li2 Kristus maimba memba alvpa, memba Griknindna moana, wo eva Hipruna moanamba os alv, Mesaia. Heva os plalva mongal lohv, indhanariniva nomba temba Sesoava kikih vrenamba, Sesoanindmba lopshalmba. Noinda pimba osva uv, Yesusva Kristusalm lohv.
\li1 \bd Kruse \bd*\rq (Yon 19:17 / Aposel 2:23) (diwai kros / saliv / lepethalt)\rq*
\li2 Memba Romnindna wevsa doara luhunna, osva indhanariniva sahoklalnonoa lohvnamba, wo hemba sena wikleihivna lepethaltra, osm dahara. Devitva honamba nihsesoamomba ten ishona hevna Tombai Sangalmora \it (Buk Song / Psalms), Sapta 22.\it* Sesoasongol Devitmba wuhho ovravna, nonapopol himba novol vewol vena.
\li1 \bd Laion \bd*\rq (Poaitamoa 4:7 / 5:5)\rq*
\li2 Laionmba eva sahoklal ovovnata, indhanamba hovra hilhala viv. Wo noinda osva an eva hemba kevravav. Yakoppa hevna ombolmba Yutamba olhna, laion maim \it (Stat 49:8—9).\it*
\li2 Yon moalamangnindrini Yesusm olhmonamba olhinvna, os himba laionmsna lohv Yutatindina \it (Poaitamoa 4:7 / 5:5).\it* Memba osm, himba doa Setanmba wohkuvhoana, hevna indhanakoklanahonam.
\li2 Pita moalamangnindrini Setanm olhmonamba olhinvna, os himba lohmana vev, os laion ten tatam silelvm. \it (1 Pita 5:8)\it*
\li1 \bd Lepat \bd*\rq (Poaitamoa 13:2)\rq*
\li2 Lepatva eva laionna nihna ovovnata mongnindna pethara, huiva owai PNGrava.
\li1 \bd Livai \bd*\rq (Hipru 7:5, 9, 10 / Poaitamoa 7:7)\rq*
\li2 Livaiva Yakopna ombol lohna, mongo Yutanindna simbel. Sesoava Livaitindimba kikih vewol vena, hevna andraram. Noinda indkumbiva sembayang andranindilmba kekal vethana Livaitindiva.
\li1 \bd Lohohmoa \bd*\rq (Kisim Bek 20:117 / Matiu 12:1-2)\rq*
\li2 Memba Sesoana lohohmoa, noi ten Sesoa Mosesm Sainai olora ovrahonam.
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Petiva lohohmoriniva\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Lopshav \bd*\rq (2 Pita 1:1,11 / 1 Yon 4:14) (kisim bek)\rq*
\li2 Honamba moamba osm lohv, Yesusva pimba lopshav, manara, pivva suwekembelmonara lovahv, plalva lovahv, pivva indkokla vina.
\li1 \bd Lot \bd*\rq (Stat 11:31 / Luk 17:28-32 / 2 Pita 2:7)\rq*
\li2 Lotva Aprahamna umbeindil lohna. Nonamba Aprahamba Urkembellini gavnamba Keinanpetharam, himba ella hevna umbeindilmba Lotmba waingana. Heva os Lotva alm vevna dom Sotom kembellam, ten indhanakokla avnam, manara, pethava hevm besalangas lohvna.
\li2 Doa sismba Sesoava suwenam tasowa pipahawolalm vevna Sotomnindm eva Gomoranindm, himba hevna ovsongolnindrini samblam unna, yeoa Lottatanamoa elapsho nominioa. Heva os Lotna ongalva nengavnang piprinna no kembellam, wo noinda hemba honalm nilhana \it (Stat 18-19).\it*
\li1 \bd Mana \bd*\rq (Kisim Bek 16 / Yon 6:31, 49 / Hipru 9:4 / Poaitamoa 2:17)\rq*
\li2 Nonamba Israelnindva sahalpetharava lovahmana vilimbvnamba, Sesoava hemba di innemba dahwol vena, os ningthivna, mana. Mana osm uv Hipruna moanamba, mani dihi memba hevpa?
\li1 \bd Manase \bd*\rq (Stat 41:50—52)\rq*
\li2 Himba Yosepna yivaltowond lohna. Plalva osm lohv, duus vevmoa.
\li1 \bd Mastet \bd*\rq (Matiu 13:31-32 / Mak 4:31-32)\rq*
\li2 Mastetva eva besal vilovta inne. Mastetkulva silel vilov, sahaikna nihna. Himba timba owai, heva os osonnamba himba kuvhoawol vev.
\li1 \bd Mel endalhui \bd*\rq (Luk 8:31 / Poaitamoa 9:1-2 / 2 Pita 2:4 / Yut 6) (hul i no gat as / hul i tudak nogut tru)\rq*
\li2 Memba vuhemba, noi ten Sesoa tihsongom noinda wolasiha vawovm, hukum vewolalm.
\li1 \bd Melkisetek \bd*\rq (Stat 14:17—20 / Hipru 5—7)\rq*
\li2 Melkisetekva mongo Sesoana sembayang andranindrini lohna doara.
\li1 \bd Memba kata ka. / Kava He. \bd*\rq (Yon 8.24, 28,58 / 18:5-6) (Mi Yet Mi Stap Olsem / em mi tasol)\rq*
\li2 Hona moara Yesusva hevmba ambara ovrana, osva kava Sesoa lohv. Manara, himba Sesoam ongavna, Sesoa hev ten hevm Mosesm ambara ovathamnanam \it (Kisim Bek 3:13-15).\it*
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Yawe\bd* eva \bd Arana ombol\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Meme\bd*
\li2 Memba mongo Yutanindna deuvtata. (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Sipsip\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Mendekliandra \bd*\rq (Matiu 8:1-4) (mirakel)\rq*
\li2 Yesus eva hevna moalamangnind mendekliandrava mindnam vewol vivna, indhanam kolvrowolalm, osm indkumbiva wiyera avra, osva honamba moamba Sesoanamini wonvruwul prov.
\li1 \bd Mesaia\bd*
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Kristus\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Moa Ishomnav Tanamolnam. / Moa Waieuk Vrev. / Moa Waiomokalthav. \bd*\rq (mekim kontrak / nupela kontrak) (Stat 6:18 / 9:1, 9 / Mak 14:24 / Galesia 3:15 / Hipru 9:15)\rq*
\li2 Memba moamba osm uv, tok promis, o kontrak.
\li2 Sesoava seilva Noatatanam awothowol vena, ona, kava yemba venglahav, pueumbva snamba si owai \it (Stat 6:18 / 9:1,9).\it* Hengava hona pethamba pueumbnamba kava si indkokla vrevavmoa.
\li2 Sesoava seilva Apraham moamba waieuk vrena, omnana, kava si tanamolnam yemba venavav, vera, petham kovorahora, eva osoa yena vera, simbepolpev mindnam phora \it (Stat 17:1-8).\it*
\li2 Wo osoa henga sism Sesoava Mosesm waieuk vrena, omnana, kava si tanamolnam Israelnindmba kolvrowol vevav, himba keknamba kana lohohmomba engitava \it (Kisim Bek 19:4—6 / 24:4—8).\it* Wo heva os owai, manara, pimba indhanamba eva es Sesoana nengavnangmba engivav, noinda heva Kristusnanangas pimba wuvolva avav.
\li2 Wo eunillamba Sesoava moamba pim ovlahinna, ona, himba nomba temba Yesus Kristusmba undnahonamba lovahthamnavrava, kava si hemba lopshavav \it (Matiu 26:28 / Rom 11:27 / 1 Korin 11:23—25 / 2 Korin 3:6 / Hipru 6:16—20).\it*
\li1 \bd Moalamangnind \bd*\rq (Matiu 10:1-4 / 28:18—20) (aposel)\rq*
\li2 Memba Yesusna andranind moashulnind 12pelara lovahvna.
\li1 \bd Moaptindi \bd*\rq (Rut 1:1)\rq*
\li2 Memba mongo Yutanindna ungund avna.
\li1 \bd Moashulnind \bd*\rq (Matiu 5:17 / Aposel 3:18 / Rom 1:2) (profet)\rq*
\li2 Memba Sesoana andranindva, ten Sesoava hevna doaramini moamba ovrahunnamba, gumai vovhoalmba vavawonam Yutanindram.
\li1 \bd Moses \bd*\rq (Kisim Bek 3:110 / Matiu 8:4 / Yon 1:17)\rq*
\li2 Mosesva Aronna boasalal lohna. Sesoava hevmba ambara vethamnana Mosesmba, os maim ona, suwe talahaprav tivtandasra sena, heva os owai, wohtavnamoa. Wo moalamang no suwemarini opiemnana, Moses, yeoa garava, kana Israelnindmoa wonpho Isiprinioa, himba kinmba mendekli vruwuv.
\li2 Mosesva Sesoana tombaimomba seilva 5pelara novol vewol vena. Sismba Yesusva hevmba numhana no tombaira, ten Moses 5pelara novol vewol venam, eva noi, ten Devit kuwulna tombai sangalmoa, eva moashulnindna tombaimom.
\li2 Manara, nonamba Yesusva men hui mendah andrava vungu vevna, hevna moalamangnindva honamba tombaimomba mendah novol vewol vinamoa, memba pimba osva ningthivpa, Besal Nemelmoa o Nupela Testamen.
\li2 Varisinindva Yesusmba os umnivna, kava Mosesna moamangas engiv, mongova owai.
\li1 \bd Nambai eunillam, nonamba ovi pethaiva imhara evhowolvram. \bd*\rq (Yon 6:39—44 / Aposel 2:17 / 2 Timoti 3:1 / Hipru 1:2 / 9:26 / 10:25) (las dei)\rq*
\li2 Seilva doarava Yutanindna moashulnindva os uvna, nambai eunillam Kristusva si provav, pimba lopshalmba.
\li2 Wo heva os Yesusna moalamangnindva henga nomba moamba weihaloh vrina, os daipotam memba, nonamba pimba Kristusnindva hemba nengviluwuvpa, prolmba hengamba, indkumbim lesvhoawolalmba.
\li1 \bd Nikolastatana \bd*\rq (Poaitamoa 2:6,15) (lain bilong Nikolas)\rq*
\li2 Nikolasva mongo gurudaspol doara lohna, wo monglava Kristusnindva hemba patvmonavna. Heva os himba doa owolokovvna.
\li1 \bd Nineva \bd*\rq (Yona 1:2)\rq*
\li2 Memba kotamendekli lohna Asiriapethara, Sesoava dom Yonamba wolaihangana hevna moashulnindrinimba, ongawolalmba hemba. Ninevanindva himba Israelnindna ungundalm einvna, heva os himba hevm weihaloh vewol vivna, wo Sesoava hemba indkokla vewol venamoa.
\li1 \bd Noa \bd*\rq (Stat 5:29)\rq*
\li2 Memba moamba os hilliv Hiprumonamba, kolvrowol vev.
\li1 \bd No moashulnindrini \bd*\rq (Lo 18:14—20 / Yon 1:21, 25 / 6:14 / 7:40 / Matiu 11:14) (dispela profet mipela i wetim)\rq*
\li2 Yutanindva os ningvna, Sesoa si mongom moashulnindrinim homba petharamba wolaihapravav, wo himba si os moakus unvav, Kristusva doa murapeta prolm vev. Wo noinda Yutanindva osva olvohvna, pimba no moashulnindrinim aevulmanav.
\li1 \bd Not \bd*\rq (Stat 4:16)\rq*
\li2 Memba moamba os hilliv Hiprumonamba, lohmanangas vev. Manara, Keinva diva ambo lohmanangas vevna no petharava.
\li1 \bd Oliv denwit \bd*\rq (Stat 8:11 / Rom 11:17, 24 / Yems 3:12 / Poaitamoa 11:4)\rq*
\li2 Olivpa movolva besal kethav. Movolva kelvwol viv, welelm, welva nomba beswonam hlav, eva osoa nihm selvowolalm obatram, eva osoa huhmohram. Yutanindva honna kelvwol vivna, englanamba owai.
\li1 \bd Ombandhana andranind \bd*\rq (1 Korin 7:20—24 / Evesus 6:5-9) (wokboi nating o wokmeri nating)\rq*
\li2 Honamba indhanamba himba ambo nisandra viv kuwulna moara. Eva henashara himba poaitava lelga vevra?
\li1 \bd Oniks \bd*\rq (Stat 2:12)\rq*
\li2 Memba hon besal, diva mendekli lohmanav.
\li1 \bd Ovsongolnind\bd*
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Sesoana ovsongolnind\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Pailat \bd*\rq (Matiu 27:2 / Yon 18:29)\rq*
\li2 Himba mongo mendekli duang luhunvna Yutanindna. Himba Sisana keusingi andra vevna, nomba temba king kuwulva wuleinvnamba Romnindnamba.
\li1 \bd Peniel \bd*\rq (Stat 32:30)\rq*
\li2 Honamba moamba osm lohv, Sesoana novlomossis.
\li1 \bd Pero \bd*\rq (Stat 12:15)\rq*
\li2 Honamba moamba osm lohv, kuwul mendekli, Isipnindna moana.
\li1 \bd Pethanind \bd*\rq (Yon 1:29 / 7:7 / 8:12, 23 / 14:17) (ol manmeri bilong graun)\rq*
\li2 Hona moarava Yonmba moalamangnindrini indhanamba hona pethanindmba pusvund vena, ona, himba Sesoamba und vivmoa. Noinda Yesusva osva unna, yenamba arapevpa luhunv Setan \it (Yon 8:44).\it*
\li1 \bd Petiva lohohmoriniva \bd*\rq (Kisim Bek 25:10 / Hipru 9:4 / Poaitamoa 11:19)\rq*
\li2 Memba petiva besal hevm snal i, Sesoana hevna moara honamba petiva kueindina. Nom lohohmom hengam nengvhoalm, ten Sesoa Mosesm ovrahonam di Sainai olora.
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Lohohmoa\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Pona poswol vinv. \bd*\rq (Matiu 3:13) (baptais)\rq*
\li2 Memba pina Kristusnindna wevsa, pona poswol velmba.
\li1 \bd Rahap \bd*\rq (Hipru 11:31 / Yems 2:25)\rq*
\li2 Himba mongo ungevlirini monarini ambo avna. Heva os himba beswonam vewol vena Israelnindna nongalpethanindrini samblamba. Himba komawohana hemba hevna deuvra, manara, hev undva vrena, osva Israelnindna Sesoava, Sesoanonoa woheinv.
\li1 \bd Rom \bd*\rq (Aposel 28:14-16) (biktaun Rom)\rq*
\li2 Romba mendekli kotava lohv Italipethara, kuwul mendekliva henamba os ningthivna Sisa. Nonamba Yesus Kristusmba lingvnamba, Romnindva daosva ohomana vevna, osva hindmongo, hindmongo, wo daosmba himba kuvhueivnamba, petham kanothongavna hevelm. Yutanindva eva di Romnind wulavnata, wo heva os himba engalpingalm vivnata Romnindmba.
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Sisa\bd*.)
\li3 \bd Romnindrininonoa\bd* \it (Aposel 16:37) (nem bilong man i stap rait long buk) Indhanariniva mongova Romnindrininonoava lohtava, polisika valgonindka hemba nisva bui vivavmoa lilnamba. Hemoa boasna wetatmora waiishuvra.\it*
\li3 \bd Tovolsangal diav.\bd* \it (Kolosi 2.15 / Evesus 4.8) (ol man i winim pait na i kam) Eva Romnindva tovolsangalva diaomana vevnata. Nonam vivna, daosram hev ten kekaiv vivnam, wo os ningiamb vevna domba deuvramba, owalm deuvnindm nongalalm.\it*
\li1 \bd Sahokla vev. / Sahonam vev. / Indkokla vev. \bd*\rq (Matiu 1:21) (sin / rong / sala)\rq*
\li2 Plalva men lohv, pivva pimba huiva ayiskos vevpa deuvrava, wo eva pivva Sesoana novrava lehrava vivmoata. Yesusnanangas pivva vi vovhueivav.
\li1 \bd Sainai \bd*\rq (Kisim Bek 19—20 / Galesia 4:21-31)\rq*
\li2 Memba mongo olo, no olorini Mosesva Sesoana moamba wulpiheinna.
\li1 \bd Samaria \bd*\rq (Luk 10:25—37 / Yon 4:4—42)\rq*
\li2 Memba mongo petha murapeta Yutanindna petharava luhunvna. Simbehumunilva henamba Yutanind, heva os himba ongamba evrowolvna Yutanindna meisungundmongo. Noinda Yutanindva hemba muskva vinvna.
\li1 \bd Samson \bd*\rq (Hetman 14-16 / Hipru 11:32)\rq*
\li2 Himba daosnindna kuwul Yutanindnamba luhunna.
\li1 \bd Samuel \bd*\rq (Aposel 3:24 / 13:20 / Hipru 11:32)\rq*
\li2 Himba mongo Yutanindna moashulnindrini luhunna. Himba Devitmba kuwulalmba awona Sesoana moara \it (1 Samuel 16:13).\it*
\li1 \bd Saptu \bd*\rq (Stat 2:1-3) (sarere)\rq*
\li2 Saptuva mongawa mingunam lohol vev. Sesoa hevelm kanothona no mingum, no mingum, osangas, osm Yutanindva sembayang vewuvmonavra. Noinda osva ningthivna, vah iaevulokomba. Daipotava pimba Kristusnindva vahva iaevulv minguramangas, sembayang venalm. Manara, Kristusva hengava phona minguram.
\li1 \bd Sara \bd*\rq (Stat 17:15 / Rom 4:19, 9:9)\rq*
\li2 Honamba moamba osm lohv, kuwulna ongal. Sarava Aprahamna ongal ana. Seilva Sarai maim alvna, wo henga Sesoa Sara maimba awona. (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Apraham\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Satusi \bd*\rq (Matiu 22:23 / Aposel 23:6—8)\rq*
\li2 Honamba monglava indhanamba, himba Yutanind, himba nom Mosesna tombaimomba 5pelarinimangas wohengivna. Himba os ningvna, ovsongolnindva avmoa, wo eva indhanamindva hengava pulvovavmoa pokamariniva.
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Yutanindna kuwul\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Sembayang andranind\bd*
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Tempel\bd*)
\li1 \bd Sesoa \bd*\rq (Stat 1:1)\rq*
\li2 Memba Sesoava noi, manam manam men hev venam.
\li2 Yutanindva Sesoana nihilmba alas ovna, sevra ovralmba, noinda osva uvna, mendekli. Nonamba Pitava Yesusmba mendekli maimba osva sevranamba, Yesusva indkvethavna hevpa. Manara, Pitava doa nonora lohvna, osva Yesusva Sesoa lohv \it (Matiu 16:16).\it*
\li3 \bd Sesoasongol\bd* \it (Stat 1:1 / Matiu 1:18) (spirit bilong God) Pimba os ningthiv, Sesoava mongasal einv, heva os undva samblamong, vei aral, vei ombol, vei meississongol. Meississongolva himba nihhui, heva os himba indhanana nihmera siheku vinv, nomba temba Yesustindilmba lovahvpa. Wo pivva manimani hevnapopol viv beswonamba.\it*
\li3 \bd Sesoana nemeltindi\bd* \it (Matiu 6:33) (kingdom bilong God) Englisnamba os pimba uv, kingdom of God. Memba pimba Kristusnind, wo Sesoana englisra pivva huiva av, wo eva si sewonamba senakembellava osta.\it*
\li3 \bd Sesoana ovsongolnind\bd* \it (Stat 3:24 / Matiu 1:20 / Luk 2:8-14) (ensel) \it* Ovsongolnindva Sesoa vewol vena, hevm wonalm senakembellam. Himba nihhui ivtovol av, noinda pivva hemba nungeilvmoa, heva os Sesoava hemba wolanga vungu vev, andram viwul venalm.
\li2 Andrava mendekliva henamba luhunvpa, pim Sesoatindim kolvrowolalm. \it (Aposel 12:6-11 / Hipru 1:14)\it* Mongnanamba Sesoava hemba wolapra vev, hevna moamba ishomnalm indhanarinim. \it (Matiu 2:13)\it* Kuwulva sambla ahai eluhunv, Maikel hev mongova \it (Yut 9),\it* eva osoa Gapriel mongova. \it (Luk 1:19)\it*
\li1 \bd Set \bd*\rq (Stat 4:25)\rq*
\li2 Honamba moamba osm lohv Hiprumonamba, otolm holvoraohv.
\li1 \bd Setan \bd*\rq (Jop 1:6 / Matiu 4:10 / Luk 10:18 / Poaitamoa 12:7-8)\rq*
\li2 Memba osm ov, Sesoana ungundrini. Manara, nonamba pimba Sesoanindva sahonamba vivpa, himba pimba wetat owol vev Sesoainda. Eva himba miva kuwulva wulluhunv tihsongonamba.
\li1 \bd Sion \bd*\rq (Matiu 21:5)\rq*
\li2 Memba mongmoa Yerusalemkota.
\li1 \bd Sipsip\bd*
\li2 Sipsippa mongo Yutanindna deuvtata. Ambo himba ovovrakolal vilov, noinda osva indhanarini heva hemba deisumbi lohmana vev. Osva vev, ilm hlalm, eva pom hlalm.
\li2 Yutanindna wevsava os luhunna, himba sipsipmba khueivna, nihilmba wohweisumbulolovna altasengra, Sesoam sembayang vinilm. Doarava Sesoava hev wohtna, vewuvmona velmba Yutanindva. Ambo hevna indkoklam leslala vewolalm. Heva verava, Kristusva pimba kilumb showol vilprovra \it (Yon 1:29, 36 / Rom 3:21-26 / Hipru 9:28).\it*
\li3 \bd Meme\bd* Memeva eva mongo Yutanindna deuvtata. Yutanindva eva hemba nona sembayang velvohmanavnata.
\li1 \bd Sisa \bd*\rq (Matiu 22:21) (Sisar)\rq*
\li2 Sisa maimba owao ovrav Romnindva osm, mendekli king kuwul kana luhunv. Yesusna novrava Romnindva annindm annindm os daos ohomana vevna, wo hengas einvna kuwulva.
\li2 Nonamba avalva Yesusmba lengvnamba, Sisa Aukustus mendekliva kuwulva einvna \it (Luk 2:1).\it*
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Rom\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Solomon \bd*\rq (Matiu 1:6—7 / 6:29 / 12:42 / Aposel 7:4—7)\rq*
\li2 Solomonmba Devitna ombol lohna. Himba aralna vuhera kuwulalmba hengava luhunvna. Wo Sesoava hemba esvema dembrahona, osva vena, di eva nowol. Himba nona vena tempelduvpa nemelva diva Yerusalemdava.
\li1 \bd Sotom \bd*\rq (Stat 13:10-13)\rq*
\li2 Sotomkembella Lotva avhoana, Aprahamna umbeindilva. Wo eva Gomorava murapeta ambo lohvnata.
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Lot\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Spen \bd*\rq (Yona 1:3)\rq*
\li2 Memba mongova pethava lohna wanplombra Metiterenianda.
\li1 \bd Suwekembel \bd*\rq (Mak 9:47-48 / Matiu 3:10 / 5:22 / Poaitamoa 19:20 / 20:1115) (hel / ples paia)\rq*
\li2 Memba vuhemba, noi Sesoa ten hukum vewol vawovm indhanakoklam noinda.
\li1 \bd Tamol eva brol \bd*\rq (Poaitamoa 1:8)\rq*
\li2 Honamba moamba osm olhwolv, Sesoa unna, ka vena, manam manam doa tumbvena, eva si manam manam wohkik vera.
\li1 \bd Tasis \bd*\rq (Yona 1:3)\rq*
\li2 Memba kota lohna Spenpethara wanpethalla nohalm. Hevm hivema lohvna, Yutanindna petharava.
\li1 \bd Tempel \bd*\rq (Matiu 4:5 / 27:51 / Yon 2:14)\rq*
\li2 Memba Yutanindna mongahvhoralm mendekli sembayangduvpa luhunv. Himba doara luhunna Yerusalemkotara. Di sembayangnind himba Sesoam sembayangelm atonglalvohmanavna. Andranind di deuvtatam weisumblolovna, andranindva nomba os nengsmoa uv, pris. Katekisva himba eva di indhanamba numhowol vewuvna tempelpulmera.
\li1 \bd Tempeltih \bd*\rq (Yon 10:22) (bikpela de bilong lotu)\rq*
\li2 Memba tihva mongo Yutanindna mendeklitihva doara lohawol lohvna, Yutanindva tempeltihva vivnamba, henga ningminivnamba, nom doaraminim, temba seilmba eindhumunva tempelmba pusvinamba, wo henga saivona, sembayang vewuvnam.
\li1 \bd Tendoriniva nomba temba Yesusva und vevnamba hemba. \bd*\rq (Yon 13:23)\rq*
\li2 Hona moarava Yon moalamangnindrini hevm opusvundthovna, heva os hevna nihilva novol venamoa.
\li1 \bd Tihsongo \bd*\rq (Kolosi 2:15) (ol strongpela spirit na kain kain samting i gat strong)\rq*
\li2 Tihsongova himba Setanna owal, himba pimba monakoklaram weiha suvwolm viv. Heva os pivva nonora lovahv, osva Sesoava doa hemba tolpiapahana. Kristusva vena honamba heva krusenana.
\li2 Seilva himba Sesoana ovsongolnind avna hevindava. Heva os Setan hemba kangal ipihana hevnahonam. Noinda pimba hemba osva nengsmoa uv, tihsongo.
\li2 Himba suwekembellam olongov. Heva os hev umnina Kristusm, ata ye lilnam kam dom wolanga vevav. Noinda mendah nambaiva prunvmoa, kamba domba \it (Matiu 8:2829).\it*
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Mel endalhui\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Tinanal \bd*\rq (Poaitamoa 5:1) (gris bilong kandel)\rq*
\li2 Nonamba Yonna moalamangnindrinina novrava, tombaiva himba novol vewol vina tombaitokolla. Wo dind vewol vivna, mulmba tinana henga sithawol vivna. Osm ata homeis mongo indhanarini pevhoarava, nonglavm.
\li1 \bd Tinen teteihnungna \bd*\rq (Matiu 2:11 / Luk 1:8-11 / Poaitamoa 5:8) (paura bilong kamapim smok i gat gutpela smel)\rq*
\li2 Memba sanda teteihnungna.
\li1 \bd Topi\bd*
\li2 Topina plalva sambla.
\li3 (1) \it (1 Pita 5:4)\it* \it (nambawan prais tru)\it* Memba osm, yimba doa Setanmba kuvhoana, Sesoana vuhera phona.
\li3 (2) \it (Poaitamoa 14:14)\it* \it (hat gol)\it* Memba osm, yimba kuwulmsna lohv keknamangas.
\li1 \bd Undnahonam keknam lohmanav. \bd*\rq (Matiu 6:30 / 8:12) (bilip)\rq*
\li2 Memba osm, indhanariniva Sesoana tombaimomba nengvra, os tanamolnam, kaoa engvra keknam.
\li1 \bd Ungevlirini \bd*\rq (Stat 2:23)\rq*
\li2 Honamba moamba osm lohv Hiprumonamba, tendorinina nihrini.
\li1 \bd Varisinind \bd*\rq (Matiu 3:7)\rq*
\li2 Himba sembayangnind, nomba doaraminimomba Mosesnamba pathaluhunvna heinda. Himba Yesusmba hevna undnahonam lovahthamnavnamoa.
\li1 \bd Vuhemba, temba indhanamindva avpa \bd*\rq (Yona 2:2 / Matiu 16:18 / Poaitamoa 1:18) (ples bilong ol man i dai)\rq*
\li2 Memba vuhemba, noi indhanasongo noinda ten avm, nengviluwuvm nom, mendeklina lesvhoawolalm.
\li1 \bd Wainwosal denwit \bd*\rq (Yon 15 / Matiu 21:33-43)\rq*
\li2 Wainmba eva besal vilovta wesel. Wainmovpa bes vewol vev os i. Polva kelvwol viv, wainelm. Englanamba kelvwol vivnamoa, heva os monglana wolpalakand vewol viv di hevnavhorangas.
\li1 \bd Wanplomb Aembul \bd*\rq (Kisim Bek 14 / Aposel 7:36 / Hipru 11:29) (solwara Retsi)\rq*
\li2 Memba mongo wanplomb liv hovra, vena Isippetham piana, eva Israelpetham piana.
\li2 Nonamba Mosesva wongavnamba Israelnindmba Isipriniva, himba hevna alana vitiwalwolna hona wanplombmba. Wo vena, pok wohpho, os wohwonphona. Wo valgonindva Isipnindnamba sis opilkilihamnavna, wo henanam wan provna, hemba os wohmera vena, dalalm.
\li1 \bd Wit \bd*\rq (Stat 41:46—49 / Matiu 12:1)\rq*
\li2 Witva brasnanihna ovona, nonam plawamba viv bretalmba.
\li1 \bd Yakop \bd*\rq (Stat 25:26)\rq*
\li2 Honamba moamba osm lohv, munngulval kevrav, Hipruna moana. Yakoppa himba Isakna ombol lohna.
\li1 \bd Yawe \bd*\rq (Stat 2:4 / Kisim Bek 3:13-15 / Matiu 4:7)\rq*
\li2 Memba Sesoana nihilnonoa. Seilva nemetva Sesoava Mosesmba ishomnana, osva kanamba nihilnonoava Yawe lohv. Hipruna moanamba memba osm uv, memba kata ka, kava wohav osangas yunalm yunalm.
\li2 Mongnanamba Yesusva hevna nihilmba os sevra ovravna, memba kata ka. Noinda pimba osva nonora lovahv, himba Sesoa lohv \it (Yon 8:24,28,58 / 18:5—6).\it*
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Arana ombol\bd* eva \bd Memba kata ka\bd*.)
\li1 \bd Yeremaia \bd*\rq (Matiu 2:17 / Matiu 27:9)\rq*
\li2 Yeremaiava mongo Sesoana doaramini moashulnindrini lohna.
\li1 \bd Yerusalem \bd*\rq (Matiu 2:1)\rq*
\li2 Memba Yutanindna mendekli kota luhunv. Hengava weihaloh vrivpa, os alv Sion \it (Poaitamoa 14:1).\it*
\li1 \bd Yesus \bd*\rq (Matiu 1:21)\rq*
\li2 Memba moamba osm uv, lopshalnindrini.
\li1 \bd Yivaltowond \bd*\rq (Stat 25:25 / 25:29—34)\rq*
\li2 Israelnindna wevsava os luhunvna, yivaltowond kuwulva wulluhunvna. Esauva indkokla vena, himba hevna boasalalmba oresvhona yivaltowondalm.
\li1 \bd Yona \bd*\rq (Matiu 12:39—41)\rq*
\li2 Yonamba mongo Sesoana moashulnindrini lohna doara.
\li1 \bd Yopa \bd*\rq (Yona 1:3)\rq*
\li2 Memba kembel lohvna Israelnindna pethara wanpethalla.
\li1 \bd Yosep \bd*\rq (Stat 30:24)\rq*
\li2 Himba Yakopina Reselina yivaltowond luhunna. Yosepna boasalal mongasal lohna, nihilva Bensamin.
\li1 \bd Yosua \bd*\rq (Aposel 7:45 / Hipru 4:8) (Josua)\rq*
\li2 Yosuava Mosesna vuherava hengava luhunna Israelnindna kuwulalm. Sahalpetharini wonphonamba, Keinanpetharam wongavna, dom ten Sesoa os unnam, yimba si pevm wohvaohuthuvav.
\li2 Wo doa Yosuava kukunvna pethava nomba Yakopna simbepolmba, temba 12pelarava phonamba, hindtindim, hindtindim, hindtindim. Lehra vethanamba, venamba, Livaitindiangas lovahvna himba pethahuiva, manara, himba Sesoana sembayang andranindilm avna. Noinda owalva ambo hemba dahwol vivna.
\li1 \bd Yotan \bd*\rq (Stat 13:10 / Matiu 3:5)\rq*
\li2 Memba mongo pomba liv Israelnindna pethara, Keinanpethara.
\li1 \bd Yuta / Yutia\bd*
\li2 Yuta mongo Yakopna ombol lohna. Yakopna ombolva 12pelara phona, wo indakonda himba pethava akokomong vena hevmba diva Keinanpetharava nominiva, nonamba Sesoava temba wonpronamba Isippethariniva. Sesoava doa doara unna, wo kuwulva nom moam wohengivna, nonamba pethamba akokomong vinvnamba.
\li2 Yutatindi mongnahalmba pethava vaohuthuna, os alvna, Yutia, wo Yerusalem kotava di lohvna no provinsra. Wo sismba nomba moamba Yuta ambo os hilvnisna mongawatilm Yakopna 12pelara towandal, hevtindinahonam.
\li2 Devit king kuwulva luhunna no Yutatindiriniva, wo eva Yesus Kristusva no Devittindirini lohna, manara, avalva Yutatindirini einna.
\li1 \bd Yutanindna Innetih\bd*
\li2 Yutanindnamba men luhunv nambaiva mendekliva innetihriniva.
\li3 (1) Mendekli tihva lohv, nonamba Sesoana tempelduvpa hengava vilivhueinvnamba diva Yerusalemrava. Os ambo weihaloh vriv, mendeklitih woklakambarini. Hona woklamonamba ambo Yesus hevm olhmonamba olhvna, kava woklamsna luhunv pethanindmba. \it (Yon 9:5)\it*
\li3 (2) Pasova Tih Memba tihva noi hevm mendeklinonoa. Nom nengvhoalm hengam, ten Sesoa muehnam Israelnindm henga. Nonam Sesoana ovsongolnindrini Isipnindna yivaltowondm kokopinvnam, Yutanindnamba kuelwolkoho vinvna. Noinda osva ningthivna, mendekli tihva kuelwolkohorini.
\li3 (3) Tihva Roti Yishuirini. Nonamba Yutanindva Isipriniva pulvovnamba, eva henanam ata rotiva tevwol vinta yisnahonamba, owai. Manara, lelnam phopianam hev Isiprini Sesoana moara. Wo noinda hlavna nomba rotiva yishuiva, no henga nengvhueivnam, ten hev pulvovnam Isiprini. Honamba nonam velvohv, Pasovatih mendekli vivm.
\li3 (4) Tihva Memba Lilmbduvrini. Hona nambainamba Yutanindva und lothopralohvna, noinda doa andrava engla poswulna, doa innemba vralm vevna osoriniva. Himba lilmbduvrava nom lehalvohvna, ten doara simbehumunil aevulinnam di sahalpethara, nonamba Isipriniva monamba ambvnamba.
\li3 (5) Pentikos Tih Honanamba Yutanindva doa indkvithivna, noinda doa witva vravna osoriniva nihilangas. Nom henga nengvhoalvohvna, ten Sesoa hena lohohmom vrahunnam hevna simbehumunilm Sainai olora. Heva os daipotava pivva Kristusnindva nom nengvhoalvohv, ten Sesoasongol holvopinnam, Kristustindim pilivhoawolalm \it (Aposel 2:4).\it*
\li1 \bd Yutanindna kuwulnind \bd*\rq (Yon 1:19)\rq*
\li2 Yon pimba ishunv, osva mindnam Yutanindna kuwulva himba Yesusmba wusapramana vinivna. Manara, Yesusva henamba indkoklamba velokusa vinvna.
\li2 Monglava nomba kuwulva himba \bd Varisinindilm\bd* lovahvna, monglava himba sembayang andranindilm lovahvna, os nengsmoa uv, \bd pris\bd*, monglava himba \bd katekis\bd* o \bd gurugama\bd* lovahvna.
\li2 Monglava himba Satusilm lovahvna, eva monglava himba polisimsna lovahvna, henoi ten tempelduvm kekalvho vrelvohvnam.
\li2 Nonamba kuwulkuwulva kusovnamba mundilnahonamba, hemba os seviluv, Sanhedrin (kaunsil) \it (Matiu 26:57—59 / Mak 14:53—55 / 15:1 / Aposel 4:1 / 23:1-8).\it*
\li2 (Yeoa nunglivm \bd Satusi / Varisi / Katekis / Gurugama / Pris\bd*.) 
